
Topic: NOS/HELP

FujiNet NOS Online Help System

Usage:

HELP [TOPIC][/SUBTOPIC]

The HELP system displays text
documents stored on Github. There-
fore, the help system is unavailable
if the FujiNet has no access to the
Internet.

Issuing the HELP command by itself
will display a list of general
topics.

Typing HELP TOPIC (where "TOPIC" is
an item in the list of topics) will
show more detail and possibly a list
of subtopics.

Finally, typing HELP TOPIC/SUBTOPIC
will show the most detail on a spec-
ific item.

Press CTRL+1 to pause/un-pause the 
scrolling text.

Press ESC to exit scrolling text.

